posting_body: ['$998-$1029 / 500ft2 - Available NOW!', 'Studios on Grand Ave!', '(St Paul)', '*1/2 month free on approved applications', '© craigslist - Map data © OpenStreetMap', '628 Grand Ave near Dale St', '(google map)', '0BR / 1Ba 500ft2 available now', 'Studios $998-$1029 Available NOW!', 'Hardwood floors, large windows, walk in closets and a separate kitchen space.', 'Building Features:', '-Newly renovated common areas, fresh paint, renovated hardwood floors and new carpets.', '-Patio/balcony on each floor.', '-Maintenance/management on site', '-After hours maintenance hotline', '-Amazing location on Grand Ave, minutes from downtown, bus stop next door, close to 94 and 35E', '-Historic charm', '-Pet Spa', 'Located at the corner of Grand and Dale!', '628 Grand Ave St Paul, MN 55105', 'cats are OK - purrr', 'dogs are OK - wooof', 'apartment', 'laundry in building', 'no smoking', 'street parking', 'rent period: monthly', '*Cats and Dogs Welcome:', 'Monthly pet rent + deposit required', 'This historic apartment is located on beautiful Grand Avenue in St. Paul.', 'Everything you need from shopping to dining is within walking distance.', 'Enjoy life on beautiful tree-lined streets with easy access to transportation, shopping, and entertainment.', "Choose from a variety of spacious apartments with hardwood floors and lots of new extra's.", 'Each home has ample closet space and resident-accessible balconies.', 'Many apartments have been updated or completely remodeled.', 'Are you ready to make the move to Grand and Dale?', 'Call for more info!', 'show contact info', 'Set up a showing here:', '<URL>']
